      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Welcome to Patches, your immersive virtual companion experience.\LBefore
    we begin, please take a moment to read our privacy policy. By continuing, you
    acknowledge and agree to the following: What We Collect\nTo support your interactions
    with Patches, we may collect the following types of data:\nEmotional and behavioral
    interaction data\L (e.g., how often you speak, how long you engage, emotional
    tags you choose or trigger)\nDevice usage patterns\L (e.g., headset activity,
    session duration, gesture inputs)\nOptional voice inputs or textual interactions,
    if enabled\L (used solely to improve contextual responses; not stored permanently)\n\nHow
    We Use It\nYour data is used only to:\nPersonalize your companion\u2019s emotional
    responses and behavior\nImprove future updates of the experience\nEnsure smooth
    technical performance\nWe do not sell or share your data with third parties.\L
    Data stays secure and, where possible, is anonymized or processed locally on
    your device.\n\nLocal Permissions\nDepending on your platform, Patches may ask
    for access to:\nMicrophone (for interaction only when enabled)\nHeadset motion
    data (to sense engagement or presence)\nLocal storage (to remember your companion
    state)\nThese permissions are only used to support the in-world experience, not
    for external tracking or analysis.\n\nSensitive Experiences\nPatches is not a
    medical or therapeutic product.\L If you are feeling distressed or in need of
    support, please consider reaching out to a professional.\L This experience is
    designed for gentle companionship, not clinical diagnosis or intervention.\n\nYour
    Consent\nBy continuing, you consent to the above terms.\L You can choose to clear
    your interaction data or disable certain permissions at any time in the system
    settings."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
